{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/course/dd/note/4/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"mem 的小站"}},"post":{"id":"6d747d89-5423-51f9-8806-986d76ccb97a","excerpt":"1. Storage Elements and Sequential Circuit Analysis 1.1. Introduction to Sequential Circuit  按照输出函数对时序电路进行分类： 摩尔(moore) 型：输出只和前一个状态有关 mealy…","html":"<h2 id=\"anchor-3a70bff030bd1829\" style=\"position: relative;\">1. Storage Elements and Sequential Circuit Analysis<a href=\"#anchor-3a70bff030bd1829\" aria-label=\"anchor 3a70bff030bd1829 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-7af148807bd4a5cd\" style=\"position: relative;\">1.1. Introduction to Sequential Circuit<a href=\"#anchor-7af148807bd4a5cd\" aria-label=\"anchor 7af148807bd4a5cd permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/04/18/gyONWRkQ.png\"alt=\"gyONWRkQ.png\" style=\"width: 627px; \" ></p>\n<p>按照输出函数对时序电路进行分类：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>摩尔(moore)</strong> 型：输出只和前一个状态有关</li>\n<li>mealy 型：输出和输入及当前输入有关</li>\n</ul>\n<p>按照事件发生的连续性对时序电路进行分类：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>同步(synchronous)</strong> 的\n<ul>\n<li>Behavior defined by knowledge of its signals at discrete instances of time</li>\n<li>torage elements observe inputs and can change state only in relation to a timing signal (<em>clock pulses</em> from a <em>clock</em>)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>异步(asynchronous)</strong> 的\n<ul>\n<li>Behavior defined by knowledge of inputs at any instant of time and the order in continuous time in which inputs change</li>\n<li>If clock is regarded as another input, all circuits are asynchronous!</li>\n<li>Nevertheless, the synchronous abstraction makes complex designs tractable!</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-77fbe7eb00bb8a36\" style=\"position: relative;\">1.2. 离散事件模拟 Discrete Event Simulation<a href=\"#anchor-77fbe7eb00bb8a36\" aria-label=\"anchor 77fbe7eb00bb8a36 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p>可以通过<strong>离散事件模拟(discrete event simulation)</strong> 来更好的理解时序电路的时间行为。离散事件模拟的规则如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/04/18/fal07yxB.png\"alt=\"fal07yxB.png\" style=\"width: 475px; \" ></p>\n<p>我们以一个二路选择器为例：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/04/18/nYKitFyS.png\"alt=\"nYKitFyS.png\" style=\"width: 569px; \" ></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>毛刺(glitch)</strong>：或称瞬态错误。当 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span></span></span></span></span> 从 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span> 变为 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span> 时，由于非门有 0.2ns 的延迟，由 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mover accent=\"true\"><mi>S</mi><mo stretchy=\"true\">‾</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">A \\overline{S}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mord overline\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8833em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.8033em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"overline-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果把选择器的输出 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>Y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.22222em;\">Y</span></span></span></span></span> 直接连到输入 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span></span></span></span></span> 上呢？</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/04/18/JR6iiTsg.png\"alt=\"JR6iiTsg.png\" style=\"width: 585px; \" ></p>\n<ul>\n<li>这里的 Y 不仅是输出，还可以记忆电路的<strong>状态(state)</strong>。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果再多加一个<strong>反相器(inverter)</strong> 呢？</p>\n<p>时钟发生器</p>\n<h2 id=\"anchor-5b05c118405eb3ef\" style=\"position: relative;\">2. 存储元件 Storage Elements<a href=\"#anchor-5b05c118405eb3ef\" aria-label=\"anchor 5b05c118405eb3ef permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-f5bb9f6e4255f525\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.1. 锁存器 Latchs<a href=\"#anchor-f5bb9f6e4255f525\" aria-label=\"anchor f5bb9f6e4255f525 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"anchor-c79381d623de48dc\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.1.1. Basic(NAND) <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mover accent=\"true\"><mi>S</mi><mo stretchy=\"true\">‾</mo></mover><mo>−</mo><mover accent=\"true\"><mi>R</mi><mo stretchy=\"true\">‾</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\overline{S}-\\overline{R}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.9667em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord overline\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8833em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.8033em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"overline-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222e