an class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.9667em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord overline\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8833em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.8033em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"overline-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord overline\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8833em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.8033em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"overline-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> <strong>锁存器(latch)</strong> 是 0 触发的。即将 set 端置 0（<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S=0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span>，<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>R</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">R=1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span>）时 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>Q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span></span></span></span></span> 被置为 1；reset 端置 0 （<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S=1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span>，<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>R</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">R=0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span>）时 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>Q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span></span></span></span></span> 被置为 0。</li>\n<li><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mtext> </mtext><mi>R</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S=0,\\ R=0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\"> </span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span> 是<strong>禁止的(forbidden)</strong> 或者<strong>未定义的(undefined)</strong>，此时输出端 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>Q</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Q=1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span> 和 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mover accent=\"true\"><mi>Q</mi><mo stretchy=\"true\">‾</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\overline{Q}=1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.0778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord overline\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8833em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.8033em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"overline-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1944em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span> 同时成立。一般不使用这种状态。</li>\n<li>如果 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>R</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">R</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span></span></span></span></span> 和 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span></span></span></span></span> 同时从 0 变成 1，则输出是<strong>不稳定的(unstable)</strong>。如果两个与非门的实验完全相同，则输出会在 01 之间震荡，否则会稳定在 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>Q</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Q=0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span> 或 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>Q</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Q=1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span> 中的一个状态，取决于两个与非门的时延。</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"anchor-143aac5a45aa0b26\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.1.2. Basic(NOR) <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>R</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S-R</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7667em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span></span></span></span></span> Latch<a href=\"#anchor-143aac5a45aa0b26\" aria-label=\"anchor 143aac5a45aa0b26 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/04/18/1YXNEnfT.png\"alt=\"1YXNEnfT.png\" style=\"width: 338px; \" ></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/04/18/SNyhcSa0.png\"alt=\"SNyhcSa0.png\" style=\"width: 451px; \" ></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>R</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S-R</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7667em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span></span></span></span></span> 锁存器是 1 触发的。</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"anchor-e2243b8a1af8b3af\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.1.3. Clocked S - R Latch<a href=\"#anchor-e2243b8a1af8b3af\" aria-label=\"anchor e2243b8a1af8b3af permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<p>多输入一路时间信号 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span></span></span></span></span> 与 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>R</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S,R</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span></span></span></span></span> 信号作与或，可将 Basic <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mover accent=\"true\"><mi>S</mi><mo stretchy=\"true\">‾</mo></mover><mo>−</mo><mover accent=\"true\"><mi>R</mi><mo stretchy=\"true\">‾</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\overline{S}-\\overline{R}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.9667em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord overline\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8833em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.8033em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"overline-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord overline\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8833em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.8033em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"overline-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> Latch 转化为 Clocked <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>R</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S-R</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7667em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span></span></span></span></span> Latch。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/04/18/BkfC3qgA.png\"alt=\"BkfC3qgA.png\" style=\"width: 361px; \" ></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/04/18/bZAECh0w.png\"alt=\"bZAECh0w.png\" style=\"width: 226px; \" ></p>\n<ul>\n<li>这里 C 的含义可解释为<strong>控制(control)</strong> 或<strong>时钟(clock)</strong> 。当 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">C=1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span> 时才接受输入，可以改变锁存器的值；当 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">C=0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span> 时拒绝输入，无论 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>R</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S, R</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span></span></span></span></span> 给定什么信号锁存器都不保持不变。</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"anchor-41bbf8aa2f77abfc\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.1.4. D Latch<a href=\"#anchor-41bbf8aa2f77abfc\" aria-label=\"anchor 41bbf8aa2f77abfc permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<p>给 Clocked S-R Latch 添加一个反相器可以得到<strong>D 锁存器(D latch)</strong>。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/04/18/qoXKJ8B2.png\"alt=\"qoXKJ8B2.png\" style=\"width: 396px; \" ></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/04/18/ZkNJftOU.png\"alt=\"ZkNJftOU.png\" style=\"width: 227px; \" ></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">C=0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span> 时保持，<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">C=1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span> 时寄存器的值 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>Q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span></span></span></span></span> 会根据输入 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">D</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span></span></span></span></span> 而更改。</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"anchor-c520741c55eb0979\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.1.5. 锁存器的时序问题 The Latch Timing Problem<a href=\"#anchor-c520741c55eb0979\" aria-label=\"anchor c520741c55eb0979 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<p>但是，锁存器存在<strong>时序问题(timing problem)</strong>。</p>\n<p>TBD</p>\n<h4 id=\"anchor-c1befbee22cf2044\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.1.6. 锁存器的标准符号 Standard Symbols for Latches<a href=\"#anchor-c1befbee22cf2044\" aria-label=\"anchor c1befbee22cf2044 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/04/18/iFJ7MCYp.png\"alt=\"\" ></p>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-08a4aa2dd774cdb0\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.2. 触发器 Flip-Flop<a href=\"#anchor-08a4aa2dd774cdb0\" aria-label=\"anchor 08a4aa2dd774cdb0 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"anchor-a88efa81b639f15c\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.2.1. S-R 主从触发器 S-R Master-Slave Flip-Flop<a href=\"#anchor-a88efa81b639f15c\" aria-label=\"anchor a88efa81b639f15c permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/04/18/2ksxJEq7.png\"alt=\"2ksxJEq7.png\" style=\"width: 351px; \" ></p>\n<ul>\n<li>第一个触发器观测输入得到 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>Q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span></span></span></span></span> 仅在时钟信号的<strong>上升沿(positive edge)</strong> 发生，即 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span></span></span></span></span> 被置为 1 的时候。\n第二个触发器改变输出 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>Y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.22222em;\">Y</span></span></span></span></span> 仅在时钟信号的<strong>下降沿(negative edge)</strong> 发生，即 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span></span></span></span></span> 被置为 0 的时候。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>一般来说，主从触发器都存在<strong>一次性采样问题(1s catching problem)</strong>：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/04/18/WoIhiZRM.png\"alt=\"WoIhiZRM.png\" style=\"width: 672px; \" ></p>\n<p>TBD</p>\n<h4 id=\"anchor-43f35701ddb4a029\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.2.2. 边缘触发 D 触发器 Edge-Triggered D Filp-Flop<a href=\"#anchor-43f35701ddb4a029\" aria-label=\"anchor 43f35701ddb4a029 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<p>TBD</p>\n<h4 id=\"anchor-601cedbb2fdb73b7\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.2.3. 正边缘触发 D 触发器 Positive-Edge-Triggered D Filp-Flop<a href=\"#anchor-601cedbb2fdb73b7\" aria-label=\"anchor 601cedbb2fdb73b7 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<h4 id=\"anchor-a5b7db8590e1bf68\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.2.4. 触发器的标准符号 Standard Symbols for Flip-Flops<a href=\"#anchor-a5b7db8590e1bf68\" aria-label=\"anchor a5b7db8590e1bf68 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/04/18/uiJvlAgB.png\"alt=\"uiJvlAgB.png\" style=\"width: 560px; \" ></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/04/18/EfG4e0AK.png\"alt=\"EfG4e0AK.png\" style=\"width: 284px; \" ></p>\n<ul>\n<li>在不特别说明实现的情况下，我们一般认为主从触发器都存在一次性采样问题。</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#anchor-3a70bff030bd1829\">1. Storage Elements and Sequential Circuit Analysis</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-7af148807bd4a5cd\">1.1. Introduction to Sequential Circuit</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-77fbe7eb00bb8a36\">1.2. 离散事件模拟 Discrete Event Simulation</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#anchor-5b05c118405eb3ef\">2. 存储元件 Storage Elements</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-f5bb9f6e4255f525\">2.1. 锁存器 Latchs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-08a4aa2dd774cdb0\">2.2. 触发器 Flip-Flop</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Ch4 Sequential Circuits","date":null,"description":null},"fields":{"cover":null,"slug":"/course/dd/note/4/","isDoc":true,"category":"[{\"name\":\"课程笔记\",\"to\":\"/course/\"}]","propsJson":null}},"previous":null,"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"6d747d89-5423-51f9-8806-986d76ccb97a","previousPostId":null,"nextPostId":null,"navJson":"[{\"slug\":\"/course/dd\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/